# PSO-Optimized vs Fixed (α,β,ρ) Comparison — Walkthrough

## What Was Done

Implemented the **latest flowchart** (Fixed α,β,ρ) as a separate C++ program and compared it against the **old flowchart** (PSO-ACO Hybrid) to demonstrate that PSO-optimized parameters yield better path costs.

