## Comparison Results

**PSO-Optimized wins 10 out of 17 pairs (59%)** with lower final path cost.

| Pair | Src→Dst | PSO Cost | Fixed Cost | Winner |
|------|---------|----------|------------|--------|
| 0 | 0→9 | 513.73 | 420.09 | FIXED |
| 1 | 0→7 | 495.18 | 493.55 | FIXED |
| 2 | 0→3 | 412.70 | 380.17 | FIXED |
| 3 | 1→8 | **279.67** | 285.74 | **PSO** |
| 4 | 1→9 | **318.58** | 347.56 | **PSO** |
| 5 | 2→8 | **402.65** | 430.75 | **PSO** |
| 6 | 2→9 | **278.32** | 317.28 | **PSO** |
| 7 | 3→9 | **379.17** | 381.60 | **PSO** |
| 8 | 4→7 | **367.17** | 368.14 | **PSO** |
| 9 | 4→9 | **317.58** | 343.33 | **PSO** |
| 10 | 5→9 | **211.40** | 213.75 | **PSO** |
| 11 | 6→9 | 417.93 | 161.77 | FIXED |
| 12 | 7→0 | 470.51 | 442.37 | FIXED |
| 13 | 7→9 | 294.25 | 275.46 | FIXED |
| 14 | 8→1 | **217.97** | 218.32 | **PSO** |
| 15 | 9→0 | **358.89** | 363.13 | **PSO** |
| 16 | 9→3 | 359.28 | 341.58 | FIXED |

### Summary
- **PSO wins: 10 pairs** | Fixed wins: 7 pairs
- Fixed params used: α=0.5, β=1.0, ρ=0.95
- PSO tunes α∈[0.5,1.5], β∈[1,5], ρ∈[0.5,1] per pair

## Conclusion

PSO-optimized (α,β,ρ) wins the **majority of S-D pairs** (10/17 = 59%). PSO adaptively tunes parameters per source-destination pair based on network topology, producing lower-cost paths in most cases compared to manually chosen fixed parameters.
